  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 71,
      "chapterTitle": "第一章",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300065233_71_408-495",
          "range": "408-495",
          "rangeStart": 408,
          "rangeEnd": 495,
          "markText": "我父亲姓皮利普，菲利普是我的教名。幼年时，不管是这个姓氏还是我的名字，我老是说成皮普，怎么也说不完整，吐字也不清楚，于是，我索性管自己叫皮普。久而久之，皮普这个名字就叫开了。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1714615429,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-05-02 10:03:49",
          "chapterUid": 71,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=71&rangeStart=408&rangeEnd=495",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=71&rangeStart=408&rangeEnd=495"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_130_5788-5818",
      "chapterUid": 130,
      "range": "5788-5818",
      "markText": "今天是我结婚的日子，”毕蒂突然幸福地大声说，“我嫁给乔了！”",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=130&rangeStart=5788&rangeEnd=5818",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=130&rangeStart=5788&rangeEnd=5818"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_79_7298-7396",
      "chapterUid": 79,
      "range": "7298-7396",
      "markText": "各位读者，读到这里请暂停一下，好好思考一下，你的人生长链条也许是铁铸的，也许是金锻的，或是缠绕着荆棘，或是开遍了鲜花，如果你没有在一个难忘的日子里亲手铸出第一环，那往后余生，它都不会成为你的束缚。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=79&rangeStart=7298&rangeEnd=7396",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=79&rangeStart=7298&rangeEnd=7396"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_88_11957-12005",
      "chapterUid": 88,
      "range": "11957-12005",
      "markText": "我当时抬头望着天上的星星，只觉得它们寒酸又卑微，只能把星光洒在乡野，而我正是在这片乡野里长大的。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=88&rangeStart=11957&rangeEnd=12005",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=88&rangeStart=11957&rangeEnd=12005"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_74_5324-5333",
      "chapterUid": 74,
      "range": "5324-5333",
      "markText": "乔又给我舀了些肉汁",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=74&rangeStart=5324&rangeEnd=5333",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=74&rangeStart=5324&rangeEnd=5333"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_71_907-935",
      "chapterUid": 71,
      "range": "907-935",
      "markText": "他们没有和世人一样为了生活苦苦挣扎，而是早早打了退堂鼓。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=71&rangeStart=907&rangeEnd=935",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=71&rangeStart=907&rangeEnd=935"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_74_4856-4865",
      "chapterUid": 74,
      "range": "4856-4865",
      "markText": "乔又给我舀了些肉汁",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=74&rangeStart=4856&rangeEnd=4865",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=74&rangeStart=4856&rangeEnd=4865"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_106_7483-7504",
      "chapterUid": 106,
      "range": "7483-7504",
      "markText": "她对我是那么不公，给我造成了那么大的伤害。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=106&rangeStart=7483&rangeEnd=7504",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=106&rangeStart=7483&rangeEnd=7504"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_131_4588-4680",
      "chapterUid": 131,
      "range": "4588-4680",
      "markText": "我握着她的手，我们一起走出了废墟。曾几何时，我第一次离开铁匠铺奔赴远大前程，晨雾早已散尽，而此时此刻，夜晚的雾气也在逐渐消退。薄雾轻起，静谧的月光广袤无垠，我依稀看到我将与她永不分离。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=131&rangeStart=4588&rangeEnd=4680",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=131&rangeStart=4588&rangeEnd=4680"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_105_617-658",
      "chapterUid": 105,
      "range": "617-658",
      "markText": "多少个夜晚，当我独自坐望炉火，我都觉得，哪里的炉火，都不如铁匠铺和家中厨房的炉火。",
      "totalCount": 66,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=105&rangeStart=617&rangeEnd=658",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=105&rangeStart=617&rangeEnd=658"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_77_4479-4501",
      "chapterUid": 77,
      "range": "4479-4501",
      "markText": "无论他身上有什么缺点，请记住他总有好心的一面",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=77&rangeStart=4479&rangeEnd=4501",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=77&rangeStart=4479&rangeEnd=4501"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_84_2024-2089",
      "chapterUid": 84,
      "range": "2024-2089",
      "markText": "收工后，我们进屋吃晚饭，这个家和家里的饭菜显得比以往任何时候都更寒酸，在我那没有教养的心里，我就比以往任何时候都为这个家感到羞愧。",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=84&rangeStart=2024&rangeEnd=2089",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=84&rangeStart=2024&rangeEnd=2089"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_100_9567-9656",
      "chapterUid": 100,
      "range": "9567-9656",
      "markText": "真正的爱情，是盲目而忠贞，是卑微如泥土，是绝对的服从，是拿出无条件的信任，去对抗你自己，对抗全世界，哪怕那个人伤了你，你也要把自己的整颗心和全部灵魂都献给他。我就是这样去爱的！”",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=100&rangeStart=9567&rangeEnd=9656",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=100&rangeStart=9567&rangeEnd=9656"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_109_3207-3296",
      "chapterUid": 109,
      "range": "3207-3296",
      "markText": "哈维沙姆小姐派她去引诱男人，折磨他们，戏弄他们，其心可谓歹毒至极，为的就是让所有倾慕者对艾丝特拉爱而不得，但凡将自己的一颗心都托付在艾丝特拉身上的男人，最后一定落得伤心而归的惨局",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=109&rangeStart=3207&rangeEnd=3296",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=109&rangeStart=3207&rangeEnd=3296"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_74_3735-3811",
      "chapterUid": 74,
      "range": "3735-3811",
      "markText": "但是他们偏不肯饶过我，他们认为机不可失，必须把我当成话柄，不时朝我指指点点。我简直成了西班牙斗牛场的一头小牛犊，任由他们满嘴仁义道德的刺扎得我遍体鳞伤。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=74&rangeStart=3735&rangeEnd=3811",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=74&rangeStart=3735&rangeEnd=3811"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_84_1736-1793",
      "chapterUid": 84,
      "range": "1736-1793",
      "markText": "很怕一件事，那就是有一天我霉运当头，在我满身污脏、看起来最卑贱的时候，一抬眼就看到艾丝特拉从铁匠铺的一扇木窗往里看",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=84&rangeStart=1736&rangeEnd=1793",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=84&rangeStart=1736&rangeEnd=1793"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_98_5202-5289",
      "chapterUid": 98,
      "range": "5202-5289",
      "markText": "当时，我既缺乏敏锐的眼力，又没有高超的感觉，并没有意识到这全是我的错。假如我对乔好一点儿，乔在我面前也可以放松下来。我对他很不耐烦，还朝他发脾气。可即使如此，乔依然热情待我。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=98&rangeStart=5202&rangeEnd=5289",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=98&rangeStart=5202&rangeEnd=5289"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_100_5994-6048",
      "chapterUid": 100,
      "range": "5994-6048",
      "markText": "从良心上讲，我很怀疑自己是否还有去看望乔的打算。但即使我有一点儿想去，听了她的这番话，这个念头也全然打消了。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065233&chapterUid=100&rangeStart=5994&rangeEnd=6048",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3532200813ab7ffbg01387f?chapterUid=100&rangeStart=5994&rangeEnd=6048"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065233_74_3951-4045",
      "chapterUid": 74,
      "range": "3951-4045",
      "markText": "姐姐听到这话，瞪了我一眼，用责备的口吻轻轻对我说：“听见了吗？要感恩。” “孩子，尤其是要对把你一手带大的人感恩。”彭波乔克先生说。",
      "totalCount": 56,
